  "text": "The proof of Theorem 1.4, as the proof of all results in this note, is completely independent of Theorem 1.1. In fact, combining Theorem 1.4 with Anderson's Theorem 1.3 we obtain a new simpler proof of Theorem 1.1, which we will use in constructing Examples 1-3. It should be observed that while Anderson-Canary and Evans used fairly involved arguments to bypass the question of tameness, we use here the resolution of the tameness conjecture by Agol [Ago] and Calegari-Gabai [CITATION_1] in a crucial way.",
